      <title>假期结束前，追踪中国股票的 ETF 看涨押注达到高位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bullish-bets-on-china-tracking-etfs-hit-highs-before-holiday-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着在岸市场结束一周假期后于周二重新开市，股市延续涨势，在美国交易的与中国相关的 ETF 短期期权成本周一升至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/bullish-bets-on-china-tracking-etfs-hit-highs-before-holiday-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
