    <item>
      <title>130 个城市推出优惠政策 国庆假期住房销量大幅增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/china-s-home-sales-jump-during-holiday-as-130-cities-offer-perks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国为振兴房地产市场而采取的最新措施已产生立竿见影的效果，从一周假期期间的销售旺盛和买家兴趣来看，情况并非如此。但反弹能否持续则是另一回事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-07/china-s-home-sales-jump-during-holiday-as-130-cities-offer-perks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Oct 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
